We're trapped!

470
00:28:56,205 --> 00:28:57,915
We should have gone
my way!

471
00:28:57,998 --> 00:28:59,875
Cera, I'm trying
to think.

472
00:28:59,917 --> 00:29:01,251
(HUFFS)

473
00:29:05,589 --> 00:29:06,673
LITTLEFOOT: Hey!

474
00:29:07,257 --> 00:29:08,884
