00:29:52,177 --> 00:29:53,720
(GROANING CONTINUES)

489
00:29:56,723 --> 00:29:58,058
(ROARS)

490
00:29:58,308 --> 00:29:59,768
(ALL CHEERING)

491
00:30:02,020 --> 00:30:03,313
(ROARING)

492
00:30:04,856 --> 00:30:06,149
(ROARS)
(ALL GASP)

