494
00:30:08,526 --> 00:30:10,028
Let him come.

495
00:30:11,905 --> 00:30:12,906
(STRAINING)

496
00:30:14,115 --> 00:30:16,117
(CRASHING)

497
00:30:17,077 --> 00:30:18,495
(GROANING)

498
00:30:21,873 --> 00:30:23,166
(ALL CHEERING)

499
00:30:24,084 --> 00:30:25,502
(GROANS)

500
00:30:27,212 --> 00:30:28,671
